# Prescription Taxonomy

Owner: operator.

This was the initial Codex scaffold. It is preserved for reference only and is
not the canonical operator-authored taxonomy.

## V0 Prescription: Retry/Cost Loop

Trigger:

- A single model/tool step retries at least twice in one run, or
- repeated failures on the same step materially increase cost/latency.

Required output:

- severity
- root cause
- one-line fix
- evidence list
- patch artifact
- expected impact
- regression-test template

Patch artifact may be:

- unified diff
- config diff
- code snippet
- regression-test template

Non-goals:

- apply the patch automatically
- infer business correctness
- expose full prompts or sensitive tool payloads
